     <p>&nbsp;</p> 
     <p><a name="Urban" id="Urban"></a>* - The<strong> Westmont in San Francisco Program</strong> campus participates in regular earthquake training and education, and is equipped with shelter and nutrition supplies for use in the event of earthquake. <em><a href="#Readiness">[Return to Readiness section above]</a></em> </p> 
